Sharon Freundel gave a lecture on dealing with traumatic incidents at a Jewish school in Maryland on March 22 . 
 She is the wife of Barry Freundel, longtime rabbi at Washington, DC's Kesher Israel Congregation, who was arrested in October . 
 Freundel was caught filming women changing in the congregation's ritual bathroom . 
 He pleaded guilty to 52 charges of voyeurism in February and is set to be sentenced on May 15 . 
 